```
stages:
    - build
    - test
    - deploy
build_app:
  stage: build
  script:
    - echo "Run build on all branches"
static_tests:
  stage: test
  script:
    - echo "Run static tests only on feature branches"
  rules:
    - if: '$CI_COMMIT_REF_NAME == "main"'
      when: never
    - when: always
  needs: []
deploy_app:
  stage: deploy
  script:
    - echo "Run deploy only on main branch"
  only:
    - main
  needs:
    build_app
```

```
---
- hosts: web
  become: yes
  tasks:
   - name: ensure Apache is installed
     yum:
       name: apache2
       state: latest
   - name: ensure Apache is enabled and started
     service:
       name: apache2
       enabled: yes
       state: started
```
